#: ../../source/models/model_abilities/multimodal.rst:41
#: ../../source/models/model_abilities/multimodal.rst:197
msgid "Quickstart"
msgstr "快速入門"

#: ../../source/models/model_abilities/multimodal.rst:43
msgid ""
"Images are made available to the model in two main ways: by passing a link "
"to the image or by passing the base64 encoded image directly in the request."
msgstr "模型可以透過兩種主要方式獲取圖像：透過傳遞圖像的連結或直接在請求中傳遞 base64 編碼的圖像。"

#: ../../source/models/model_abilities/multimodal.rst:47
msgid "Example using OpenAI Client"
msgstr "使用 OpenAI 用戶端的範例"

#: ../../source/models/model_abilities/multimodal.rst:78
msgid "Uploading base 64 encoded images"
msgstr "上傳 Base64 編碼的圖片"

#: ../../source/models/model_abilities/multimodal.rst:121
msgid "Limiting Images Per Prompt"
msgstr "限制每輪對話中的圖片數量"

#: ../../source/models/model_abilities/multimodal.rst:123
msgid ""
"For vision models using the VLLM backend, you can use the "
"``limit_mm_per_prompt`` parameter to limit the number of images that can be "
"processed in each conversation turn. This helps control memory usage and "
"improve performance."
msgstr ""
"對於使用 VLLM 後端的視覺模型，你可以透過 ``limit_mm_per_prompt`` "
"參數來限制每輪對話中可以處理的圖像數量。這有助於控制記憶體使用並提升效能。"

#: ../../source/models/model_abilities/multimodal.rst:142
msgid "Alternatively, you can launch the model using the command line:"
msgstr "或者，你可以使用命令列啟動模型："

#: ../../source/models/model_abilities/multimodal.rst:155
msgid ""
"For Web UI, you can set the ``limit_mm_per_prompt`` parameter in the launch "
"form:"
msgstr "對於 Web UI，你可以在 vLLM 引擎表單中設定 ``limit_mm_per_prompt`` 參數："

#: ../../source/models/model_abilities/multimodal.rst:161
msgid "This parameter provides the following benefits:"
msgstr "此參數提供以下好處："

#: ../../source/models/model_abilities/multimodal.rst:163
msgid ""
"**image**: Sets the maximum number of images allowed per conversation turn"
msgstr "**image**: 設定每輪對話中允許的最大圖像數量"

#: ../../source/models/model_abilities/multimodal.rst:164
msgid ""
"Helps prevent memory overflow, especially when processing multiple images"
msgstr "有助於防止記憶體溢位，特別是在處理多張圖像時"

#: ../../source/models/model_abilities/multimodal.rst:165
msgid "Improves model inference stability and performance"
msgstr "提升模型推理的穩定性與效能"

#: ../../source/models/model_abilities/multimodal.rst:166
msgid "Applies to all VLLM-based vision models"
msgstr "適用於所有基於 VLLM 的視覺模型"

#: ../../source/models/model_abilities/multimodal.rst:169
msgid ""
"The ``limit_mm_per_prompt`` parameter only takes effect when using the VLLM "
"backend. If your model uses other backends, this parameter will be ignored."
msgstr "``limit_mm_per_prompt`` 參數僅在使用 VLLM 後端時生效。如果你的模型使用其他後端，此參數將被忽略。"

#: ../../source/models/model_abilities/multimodal.rst:171
msgid ""
"You can find more examples of ``vision`` ability in the tutorial notebook:"
msgstr "你可以在教學筆記本中找到更多關於 ``vision`` 能力的範例。"

#: ../../source/models/model_abilities/multimodal.rst:175
msgid "Qwen VL Chat"
msgstr "Qwen VL Chat"

#: ../../source/models/model_abilities/multimodal.rst:178
msgid "Learn vision ability from a example using qwen-vl-chat"
msgstr "透過使用 qwen-vl-chat 的範例來學習使用 LLM 的視覺能力"

#: ../../source/models/model_abilities/multimodal.rst:182
msgid "Audio"
msgstr "音頻"

#: ../../source/models/model_abilities/multimodal.rst:184
msgid ""
"With the ``audio`` ability you can have your model take in audio and "
"performing audio analysis or direct textual responses with regard to speech "
"instructions. Within Xinference, this indicates that certain models are "
"capable of processing audio inputs when conducting dialogues via the Chat "
"API."
msgstr ""
"通過「音頻」功能，您的模型可以接收音頻並執行音頻分析或根據語音指令直接生成文字回應。在 Xinference 中，這表示某些模型在透過 Chat API"
" 進行對話時能夠處理音頻輸入。"

#: ../../source/models/model_abilities/multimodal.rst:192
msgid ""
"The ``audio`` ability is supported with the following models in Xinference:"
msgstr "「音訊」功能在 Xinference 中支援以下模型："

#: ../../source/models/model_abilities/multimodal.rst:194
msgid ":ref:`qwen2-audio-instruct <models_llm_qwen2-audio-instruct>`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/models/model_abilities/multimodal.rst:199
msgid ""
"Audios are made available to the model in two main ways: by passing a link "
"to the image or by passing the audio url directly in the request."
msgstr "音訊可以透過兩種主要方式提供給模型：透過傳遞圖片連結，或在請求中直接傳遞音訊 URL。"

